title: Drag Formula
text: Recall the drag force formula: F $$=$$ $$\frac{1}{2} C p A v^2$$.

title: C for Skydiver
text: Recall the drag coefficient C for a skydiver is $$0.7$$, and the density of air is $$1.21$$.

title: Plug In and Solve
text: Solve for v (in $$\frac{m}{s}$$, rounded to nearest whole number): $$60\times9.8$$ $$=$$ $$1\frac{1}{2}\times1.21\times0.14 v^2$$.
